   171	        # Causal-credibility shrinkage toward the null (zero health effect),
   172	        # weight drawn from the archetype's evidence tier. A higher-credibility
   173	        # design keeps more of the literature effect; a weak/observational one
   174	        # is shrunk hard.
   175	        tier_name = a.get("causal_credibility")
