    16	# inflated to base-year dollars in the loader (CPI-U), so dollars and
    17	# cost-per-QALY inputs share one price level. Dividing nominal 2019-2025 gifts
    18	# by 2026-dollar costs would understate QALYs by ~13%.
    19	#
    20	# Philosophy (GiveWell-style): wherever possible a cost-per-QALY is DERIVED
    21	# from a causal effect estimate in the literature (cost-per-life,
