   108	  # Fixed inputs for the VQALY discount-rate rescaling. These are CALIBRATION
   109	  # CONSTANTS chosen so a flat quality-weighted annuity reproduces HHS Table
   110	  # 2's discounted PV QALYs (19.5 @3%, 11.7 @7%) to within 0.1% — they are not
