   137	      335.123/304.702 = 1.10 gives ~$4,400-$6,050 per life. A child death
   138	      averted at ~age 1 with ~65 remaining life-years, discounted at 3% with
   139	      half-cycle correction (annuity ~28.9) and utility ~0.87, is ~25.1
   140	      discounted QALYs, giving endpoints of ~$175-$241 per QALY-equivalent;
   141	      the loguniform {150, 260} widens that for conversion uncertainty
   142	      (utility, remaining years, price level). An earlier revision also used a
